 We have expanded our hybrid battery warranty to reflect our confidence in the quality,
 dependability and reliability of our products. From the 2020 model year forward,
 every Toyota hybrid battery warranty will cover 10 years from date of first use or 150,000 miles,
 whichever comes first (previously 8 years or 100,000 miles). *
